  "title": "Digital Content & E-Commerce Executive",
  "description": "<p>⭐ Job Description (Main Responsibilities)</p><p>We are looking for a creative and hands-on Digital Content & E-Commerce Executive to support our fast-growing mobile tech business. This role involves content creation, social media management, and e-commerce platform updates.</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>• Shoot and edit product photos and videos (unboxing, lifestyle, short reels)</p><p>• Create content for Instagram, TikTok, Facebook (posts, stories, reels)</p><p>• Edit videos using CapCut / Canva or similar tools</p><p>• Upload and manage product listings on Shopee and Lazada (photos, descriptions, pricing)</p><p>• Create simple marketing banners for product launches and promotions</p><p>• Assist in daily e-commerce tasks such as updating stock, product info, and campaign tags</p><p>• Support content planning and execution for phone launches</p><p>• Work closely with the team to ensure consistent branding across platforms</p><p>• Perform simple admin or marketing support tasks when needed</p><p>---</p><p>⭐ Requirements:</p><p>• 1–2 years experience in social media, content creation, or e-commerce (fresh grads with strong portfolios may be considered)</p><p>• Basic photography and videography skills</p><p>• Proficient in CapCut, Canva, or similar editing tools</p><p>• Familiar with Instagram, TikTok, and social media trends</p><p>• Creative, fast learner, and able to work independently</p><p>• Comfortable handling mobile phones and tech products</p><p>• Able to work in a fast-paced environment with frequent launches</p><p>---</p><p>⭐ Work Schedule & Details:</p><p>• Full-Time</p><p>• 5 work week</p><p>• Work Location: Midview City</p><p>• Immediate start preferred</p><p>---</p><p>⭐ Salary Range:</p><p>$2,400 – $2,800 per month, depending on experience</p><p>---</p><p>⭐ Additional Information:</p><p>• Hands-on role with daily content creation</p><p>• Opportunity to be involved in major phone launches</p><p>• Young, creative, fast-paced environment</p><p>• Training provided for e-commerce tools if needed</p><p>---</p><p>⭐ How to Apply:</p><p>Interested applicants may apply via MyCareersFuture :</p><p>• Resume</p><p>• Portfolio / IG / TikTok</p><p>• Earliest start date</p><p>• Expected salary</p>",
